    <h1>Hourglass Body</h1>

    <h2>Hourglass Body Type for Females</h2>

    <h3>Body Type Description</h3>
    <p>The hourglass body type is characterized by a balanced bust and hip measurement, with a well-defined waist. This body type typically has curvy proportions and is often considered the ideal feminine shape. Women with this body type tend to gain weight evenly throughout their bodies, but they may have a higher tendency to store fat in the hips and thighs. An hourglass figure is often associated with a proportionate, symmetrical appearance.</p>

    <h3>Food List for Hourglass Body Type Females</h3>
    <p>To support a healthy body composition and maintain muscle while managing fat distribution, a balanced diet rich in whole foods is essential. The recommended macronutrient breakdown for hourglass body types is generally 40% carbs, 30% protein, and 30% fat.</p>

